algebras are underlined. In each entry the octonionic
dimensionality  of the fundamental spinors is also
reported. The signatures admitting, for each given spacetime
dimension , spinors of minimal octonionic dimensionality are
denoted with a "". Finally, the chain of reductions from a
given maximal Clifford algebra is sketchily reported (please
notice that the chain of reductions is not necessarily unique, for
instance the  signature can be produced by erasing a
single Gamma matrix either from  or from ). We get
 
 
